gobblin.metrics

Class InnerMetricContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codahale.metrics.MetricRegistry
      • gobblin.metrics.InnerMetricContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.codahale.metrics.Metric, com.codahale.metrics.MetricSet, ReportableContext, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class InnerMetricContext
extends com.codahale.metrics.MetricRegistry
implements ReportableContext, Closeable
    Contains list of Metrics, Tags, as well as references to parent and child MetricContext for a MetricContext. This object is only references by the corresponding MetricContext as well as the RootMetricContext, and it is used to report metrics one last time after the corresponding MetricContext has been GCed.
